&lt;h2&gt;About Instabase and the Evolution of Our Business Model&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Instabase is the pioneer in helping the world’s largest enterprises—including global banks, insurance leaders, and healthcare giants—unlock and automate value from unstructured data. Our core platform is the industry standard for reading, understanding, and processing complex, unstructured documents at massive scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a strategic addition to our current business model, we are building&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;SuperApp,&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;our natively multimodal, stateful AI assistant and autonomous agent platform. SuperApp represents the next evolution of Instabase: moving from passive document extraction to active, self-correcting agentic execution. By combining our enterprise-grade document understanding with secure, real-time sandboxed code execution, SuperApp enables users to not only parse unstructured data but programmatically act on it, write and run execution scripts, orchestrate complex software tools over Model Context Protocol (MCP), and complete open-ended reasoning tasks in a secure environment.&lt;/p&gt;
